@Comment:	Time is 4:45
@Comment:	<letter one>: Hi Tanya , how are? you? I went Fishing and Geno cote Little Fish. I PlayEd with Foreus Girls on a Slide. and I climbed a ladder and fell. PS write back Chi; <letter two>; Hi Tanya How are you
@Comment:	MOT suggests writing to Tanya , a friend of Chi's who lives in Canada. Chi has written a letter to her before. Chi is dependent on Mot to tell her what to write. Mot coaches Chi , reminding her of things she has done since her last letter to Tanya. First letter is printed. Chi is very anxious to write in cursive and does so in a second letter.
